    :) :( :D :> :< :b :p :± :/ :\\ :O

    8) 8( 8D 8> 8< 8b 8p 8± 8/ 8\\ 8O

    ;< ;)

    bbl bbt brb btw rotfl rtfm l8r

  If you want to see more of these, just request one via EMail, but
 no noses please!  ;-)


